---
import MarketingLayout from '../components/layout/MarketingLayout.astro'
---

<MarketingLayout title="Cara Kerja">
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 bg-primary-50 text-primary-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4">
          Simple & Mudah
        </span>
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-neutral-900">
          Cara Kerja ManggaKu
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-neutral-500 text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto">
          Platform sederhana yang menguntungkan semua pihak — dari kebun ke meja makanmu.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="relative">
        <!-- Vertical line connector -->
        <div class="absolute left-6 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary-200 via-primary-400 to-primary-200 hidden md:block" />

        <div class="space-y-12">
          <!-- Step 1 -->
          <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-6 md:gap-10">
            <div class="relative z-10 w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-600 text-white rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-lg font-bold shadow-lg shadow-primary-500/25">
              1
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-neutral-100 hover:border-primary-100 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-primary-500/5 transition-all duration-300">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18 9v3m0 0v3m0-3h3m-3 0h-3m-2-5a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM3 20a6 6 0 0112 0v1H3v-1z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900">Buat Akun</h2>
              </div>
              <p class="text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">
                Daftar sebagai Konsumen, Petani, atau UMKM. Isi data diri dan verifikasi nomor HP kamu. Prosesnya cepat dan gratis.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Step 2 -->
          <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-6 md:gap-10">
            <div class="relative z-10 w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-600 text-white rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-lg font-bold shadow-lg shadow-primary-500/25">
              2
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-neutral-100 hover:border-primary-100 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-primary-500/5 transition-all duration-300">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-secondary-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-secondary-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900">Jelajahi Marketplace</h2>
              </div>
              <p class="text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">
                Temukan mangga segar dari berbagai varietas atau produk olahan dari UMKM lokal Indramayu. Filter berdasarkan kategori, harga, atau lokasi.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Step 3 -->
          <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-6 md:gap-10">
            <div class="relative z-10 w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-600 text-white rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-lg font-bold shadow-lg shadow-primary-500/25">
              3
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-neutral-100 hover:border-primary-100 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-primary-500/5 transition-all duration-300">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 3h2l.4 2M7 13h10l4-8H5.4M7 13L5.4 5M7 13l-2.293 2.293c-.63.63-.184 1.707.707 1.707H17m0 0a2 2 0 100 4 2 2 0 000-4zm-8 2a2 2 0 100 4 2 2 0 000-4z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900">Pesan & Bayar</h2>
              </div>
              <p class="text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">
                Pilih produk, masukkan ke keranjang, pilih alamat pengiriman dan metode pembayaran yang tersedia. Pembayaran aman dan terpercaya.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Step 4 -->
          <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-6 md:gap-10">
            <div class="relative z-10 w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-600 text-white rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-lg font-bold shadow-lg shadow-primary-500/25">
              4
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-neutral-100 hover:border-primary-100 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-primary-500/5 transition-all duration-300">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-secondary-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-secondary-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M20 7l-8-4-8 4m16 0l-8 4m8-4v10l-8 4m0-10L4 7m8 4v10M4 7v10l8 4" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900">Terima di Rumah</h2>
              </div>
              <p class="text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">
                Lacak pesananmu secara real-time. Mangga segar langsung dikirim dari kebun ke pintu rumahmu dengan packing khusus menjaga kesegaran.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 text-center">
        <a
          href="/marketplace"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 text-base font-semibold text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-primary-700 rounded-2xl hover:from-primary-700 hover:to-primary-800 transition-all shadow-lg shadow-primary-500/25 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary-500/30 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:ring-offset-2 min-h-[44px]"
        >
          Mulai Belanja
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MarketingLayout>
